{"tid":1695670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11.17交比民陣好唔好？","createTime":"2019-11-05T18:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T13:00:54.000Z","uid":104425,"like":30,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"7636d464db42847c6dc72461b5e4967df1f2a892","tid":1695670,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T18:38:18.000Z","msg":"[反對大遊行，覺得出嚟就係送頭嘅，可以上一頁]<br />\n<br />\n距離1020, 都有幾個星期<br />\n呢排係咁吹淡風<br />\n我覺得係要搞返次振士氣<br />\n冇不反唔強求百萬啦<br />\n但起碼好似1020咁上下，甚至更多人，幫大家上返電<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n10號星期日太急<br />\n24號又區選<br />\n所以17我覺得係最適合<br />\n地點冇咩所謂<br />\n<br />\n主題方面<br />\n可以聚焦公平選舉<br />\n當然五大訴求唔少得<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32fa0a2a66fec082a52fa7d1b0225b1d915c6a51","tid":1695670,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T18:44:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4c7e089cdbe060c1c50eb053cd20d8902e78888","tid":1695670,"uid":14494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T18:47:39.000Z","msg":"正常黎講1017出硬反對, 係咪照出黎先?<br />\n咁就行番112舊路, 有冇PLAN C?"},{"pid":"14f912429a816ff34697d440e161019beac4995e","tid":1695670,"uid":258003,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T18:50:20.000Z","msg":"唔好<br />\n一定唔出<br />\n勇武大晒冷行動先會出<br />\n保護和理非跑來跑去俾狗撚不斷撤退，心很累"},{"pid":"401e3e2c840afb22b80c437f92811df182acb393","tid":1695670,"uid":104425,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4c7e089cdbe060c1c50eb053cd20d8902e78888","tid":1695670,"uid":14494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T18:47:39.000Z","msg":"正常黎講1017出硬反對, 係咪照出黎先?<br />\n咁就行番112舊路, 有冇PLAN C?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T19:26:55.000Z","msg":"九龍果次其實都幾安全嘅<br />\n算四通八達"},{"pid":"b12b9e0717dc572af4cb74de9ce2f138b9473ad1","tid":1695670,"uid":54181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T19:29:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid"